OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777921886
OL,3,C14 dogs found living in squalor after
OL,4,Cowner's death
OL,6,FA fundraising appeal has been launched
OL,7,Fto fund treatment after 14 dogs were
OL,8,Ffound locked in kennels in "squalid"
OL,9,Fconditions after their owner died.
OL,11,FSeventeen birds - including finches,
OL,12,Fparrots and budgerigars - were also
OL,13,Fdiscovered by the RSPCA at the house
OL,14,Fin Whitby, North Yorkshire, after the
OL,15,Fcharity was alerted by police last
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,18,FOne of the dogs has since died. Twelve
OL,19,Fare recovering at the RSPCA in York.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
