OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777921886
OL,3,C14 dogs found living in squalor after
OL,4,Cowner's death
OL,6,FThe centre is now appealing for help
OL,7,Fto fund treatment.
OL,9,FAnimal welfare supervisor, Marie
OL,10,FSandall, said: "As a self-funding
OL,11,Fcharity, these costs are beginning to
OL,12,Fmount up for us which is why we're
OL,13,Fappealing to our supporters, who are
OL,14,Falways so wonderful in these
OL,15,Fsituations, to donate to our
OL,16,Ffundraising appeal to help us cover
OL,17,Fthe significant veterinary costs and
OL,18,Fthe dogs' ongoing care."
OL,26,@rD@POU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
