CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777921886
OL,3,C14 dogs found living in squalor after
OL,4,Cowner's death
OL,6,FRSPCA animal rescue officer Mollie
OL,7,FMasters was one of four officers from
OL,8,Fthe charity who spent several hours on
OL,9,Fthe scene after being alerted to the
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,FShe said: "The conditions on site were
OL,13,Fsqualid and extremely challenging and
OL,14,Fmany of the dogs were understandably
OL,15,Fnervous, so we had to work slowly and
OL,16,Fpatiently with them.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777921886
OL,3,C14 dogs found living in squalor after
OL,4,Cowner's death
OL,6,F"It was a very sad set of
OL,7,Fcircumstances but we're really pleased
OL,8,Fwe've been able to help these animals
OL,9,Fand the team at York are doing a
OL,10,Ffantastic job getting the dogs back to
OL,11,Fgood health so they can go on to find
OL,12,Floving new homes.
OL,14,F"This was a large and upsetting
OL,15,Fincident for us to deal with."
OL,17,FFour of the dogs had to be
OL,18,Fhospitalised overnight and needed
OL,19,Fintravenous fluids for 24 hours.
OL,20,FSeveral were severely matted in faeces
OL,21,Fand urine and had to be clipped.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
