OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777921886
OL,3,C14 dogs found living in squalor after
OL,4,Cowner's death
OL,6,FLast year the RSPCA responded to more
OL,7,Fthan 4,000 incidents across England
OL,8,Fand Wales where at least 10 animals
OL,9,Fwere found at a single address.
OL,11,FThe charity says cases of large
OL,12,Fnumbers of animals being kept at one
OL,13,Faddress can be linked to mental health
OL,14,Fstruggles, the cost of living crisis
OL,15,For breeders operating with poor
OL,16,Fpractices.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
